name: Over High Falls In A Tiny Barrel
name_original: Over High Falls In A Tiny Barrel
description:
Go over the scenic High Falls of Rochester, NY in a barrel!
Avoid birds, fish, and rocks. Stray too far and a wind gusts will toss you around.

Controls: 

Direction - Arrow Keys

Start – Enter

Good luck, Adventurer!
